      "parameters": {
        "content": "## CoreClaw Google Maps Leads - Complete Global\\n\\n1. Install `n8n-nodes-coreclaw`.\\n2. Create a CoreClaw API credential.\\n3. Select that credential on every CoreClaw node after import.\\n4. Edit Lead Search Input, then execute.\\n\\nFlow: Search scrapers -> select Google Maps keyword scraper -> get details/version/schema -> generate campaign config -> run -> poll -> results -> CSV/JSON exports -> logs.\\n\\nNo API key, local path, or proxy setting is stored in this workflow.",
